# --- Port Scan Defense (pfSense would block SYN packets) ---
# In pfSense: Add a rule to block packets with TCP SYN flag and no ACK
# (Documentation only, pfSense rules are not written in text files like Suricata)

# --- SYN Flood Detection (Suricata Rule) ---
alert tcp any any -> 192.168.10.10 80 (msg:"SYN Flood Detected"; flags:S; threshold:type both, track by_src, count 20, seconds 1; sid:1000001; rev:1;)

# --- DNS Tunneling Detection (Suricata Rule) ---
alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"Suspicious DNS Tunneling"; dns.query; pcre:"/.{50,}/"; sid:1000002; rev:1;)
